  "title": "AD&D Dragon Flyers",
  "authorName": "Simon Dorfman",
  "authorEmail": "simon@simondorfman.com",
  "notes": "Playing tips:\nPlay champions into pool right away for Favorable Winds.  Attach flyer magic items to non-flyers before event appears.\n\nPhilosophy:\nAttack and raze realms, or blow away realms with spells.  Get Remnis in play for recursive spell/realm abuse.\n\nChampions:\nDragons.  Flyers for bringing out Remnis.  AD&D for artifacts.\n\nMagic Items:\nHigh bonus to help bring out Avatars.  Lots of them for use with Loric the Fence.  Speed Bags.\n\nRealms:\nHelp in battle, help dragons, draw cards.\n\nCombos:\n-raze realm thru combat, then discard it with Dissolution, then retrieve Dissolution with Remnis to repeat next turn\n-attach Geneva Conclave to lead realm, then play Siege to destroy opposing lead realms.\n-not always the thing to do, but if during phase 2, Front Lines is the only realm in Hand, might as well play Siege before playing Front Lines.",
